# MiladyOS file_contexts.
#
# Each line: <regex> <selinux_context>. Matched against absolute paths
# during fs label assignment. AOSP applies the broader system_file label
# to /system/priv-app/Milady/ by default — extend here if Milady ever
# ships data files outside the APK that need their own type.

/data/milady(/.*)?            u:object_r:milady_data_file:s0
